        <Parent_String>wood by form or function [300012776], wood (plant material) [300011914], wood and wood by product [300011913], plant material [300124117], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
